data.description: Welcome home to this amazing 2 bed, 2 bath townhome with unfinished basement. This home has been completely remodeled to include amazing color palate and shiplap.  Fantastic living room with fireplace, large kitchen with dining area.  All kitchen appliances included and a half bath finish out the main level.  Upstairs, you will love the spaciousness of the 2 bedrooms.  Large bathroom.  unfinished basement gives you plenty of space to expand your living area.  Nice deck and private area.  1 car detached garage
